    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly pristine, collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously kept in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen inclement weather. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like luster without a single stone chip or swirl mark. Inside, the cabin is immaculate; the premium leather remains supple with no bolster wear, and the 'new car' scent is still present. Every electronic component and mechanical system functions perfectly, backed by a comprehensive, folder-thick service history. This is a rare opportunity to own a turn-key example in absolute showroom condition. No disappointments, no stories\u2014just perfection for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 48500.0,
